  "notes": [
    "Every cell varies a non-isomorphic signed angular-gap vector before an independent exact-count table is frozen; algorithm measurement seeds are separate.",
    "QGapSelect receives k only; independent IAE additionally receives the public gap floor and is a gap-aided reference rather than an information-matched baseline.",
