    "Only certified exact recovery counts as success; heuristic completions remain failures.",
    "QGapSelect versus the gap-aided independent IAE reference uses exact paired McNemar tests, fixture-pair bootstrap intervals, unconditional all-pair query differences, and Holm FWER correction across cells.",
